* Changes in 0.5 and 0.4 relative to 0.3
 ** Uses the hunchentoot-vhost package for support for virtual hosts
    (providing the ability to run multiple services based on the
    hostname used to access the web service.
 ** Uses the hunchentoot-auth package to provide user authentication
    services.
    
